Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
This brand new freestanding warehouse at 38 Bonview Circuit, Truganina, is located in Truganina’s premier industrial locale – The Crossing. This is an industrial 3 zoned estate, which boasts unrivalled proximity to the residential precinct of Truganina and Tarneit.

The current Western Road Upgrade Project will be completed in 2021. This will ensure that Palmers, Dohertys and Leakes Roads will improve efficiency of travel time for businesses operating in Melbourne’s west. Access to the city and freeway network via Leakes Road, and to the north via Palmers/Robinsons Road will be improved by this upgrade. Bonview Circuit and neighbouring Apex Drive, will eventually provide a major thoroughfare/shortcut for vehicles driving from Palmers to Forsyth Road, increasing exposure to passing traffic for this site.

Wide roads, generous landscaping and zoning restrictions, will ensure that this is a clean and desirable estate for decades to come. The Commercial 2 precincts on Leakes Road provide two important neighbouring offices, retail, food outlets and other retail amenity.

+ Total building area: 2,313sqm*
+ Two levels of corporate office and amenities of 282sqm*
+ High clearance canopy of 504sqm*
+ Four roller doors and two crossovers
+ Site area of 3,655sqm*
+ 36 car spaces

Building features:
+ Massive cubic capacity – 9.5m high concrete panels
+ Clear span warehouse 
+ Four container height motorised RSDs – 5m x 5m
+ Motorised front sliding gate
+ Three phase power
+ Corporate office over two levels 
+ Heating/cooling
+ Modern façade and landscaping
+ Racking plans are available on request
